%% Diagram: Failure handling decision tree for transcoding jobs
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    F[Job failure] --> Q1{Failure class?}
    Q1 -->|Transient: timeout, throttle| R1[Retry with exponential backoff + jitter]
    Q1 -->|Resource: encoder OOM| R2[Retry on larger instance]
    Q1 -->|Permanent: unsupported codec, corrupt| DLQ[Send to dead-letter queue]
    Q1 -->|Non-idempotent: partial upload| FAIL[Fail job - do not retry]
    R1 --> Q2{Attempts &lt; max?}
    R2 --> Q2
    Q2 -->|Yes| RUN[Re-enqueue]
    Q2 -->|No| DLQ
    DLQ --> ALERT[Alert + manual triage]
    FAIL --> ALERT
